Realistic Style: - [0-3s] A person is kneeling under a kitchen sink with a wrench; a small, shiny metal washer sits on the edge of the cabinet base.
- [3-7s] As the person reaches for it, the washer suddenly expands to the size of a bicycle wheel, emitting a low metallic hum as it defies gravity to pivot and steer itself with precision toward the drain.
- [7-10s] The washer stops rolling just short of the floor drain; the person sighs in relief and reaches down to retrieve it.
